{"tid":2156434,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方屯門打擊非法收債拘16人 票控34名圍觀賭檔者","createTime":"2020-08-14T12:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T12:35:53.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a41f442d3e1589250f3ef2292005790f2e4f769","tid":2156434,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:15:43.000Z","msg":"警方屯門打擊非法收債拘16人 票控34名圍觀賭檔者<br />\n2020-08-14 HKT 19:22<br />\n<br />\n&quot;警方在屯門區打擊非法收債，拘捕16人，又票控34名圍觀賭檔的人士。<br />\n<br />\n屯門警區總督察武少禧表示，被捕的14男2女介乎20至70歲，部分有黑社會背景，涉嫌放高利貸、刑事毀壞、刑事恐嚇、管有任何物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產、經營街頭賭博場所及街頭聚賭，警方檢獲追債紙、強力膠水、油漆及賭博工具等......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543789-20200814.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543789-20200814.htm&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcT2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=a8655065\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543789-20200814.htm&h=1da21417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543789-20200814.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f384403acbb41e65f2d6db0e41ebc81f943cbbc3","tid":2156434,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"咁又點？關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"fe76f191d3a355efcee111021d0efeab0e0b10d1","tid":2156434,"uid":16567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f384403acbb41e65f2d6db0e41ebc81f943cbbc3","tid":2156434,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"咁又點？關我撚事咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"關你撚事又點？關我撚事呀"},{"pid":"16424ac9d232f395d110193f082508ab5e07f430","tid":2156434,"uid":360248,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f384403acbb41e65f2d6db0e41ebc81f943cbbc3","tid":2156434,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:18:48.000Z","msg":"咁又點？關我撚事咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020